Class OrientedWallBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • generation.OrientedWallBoard
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HorizontalWallBoard, VerticalWallBoard

    abstract class OrientedWallBoard
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper around (not subclass of) the Wallboard class that allows for convenient access of cells adjoining the wallboard and location/removal of the wallboard in the floorplan. Abstract class that is meant to be instantiated in the VerticalWallBoard or HorizontalWallBoard classes.
    Author:
    Elijah Mas
